In terms of security, after implementing the backup strategy for deaticvate
remember to implement your network security measure!
this means that you have to know fully how is designed your network and the potential threat!

design and implement your threat model.

you can test it with nmap etc


Never open unnecessary ports!

To connect to your NAS/server always do that with a VPN
this VPN should possibly not run in the NAS but in another
dedicate machine (like a raspberrypi)
